Subject: Report showing where AD security group is applied
Description:
How do I report on where an Active Directory domain security group is applied to a file system share, folder, or file (or SharePoint)?

FSAA_GROUP_Direct_permissions_Results
I would think this job would provide the data I need, but StealthAudit locks up every time I try to view this job Results.
What_We_Know__c:
"FSAA_GROUP_Direct_permissions_Results" - Is this a custom job created by professional services?  I cannot find in in NEA v11.6 (yet?).

I can find views and tables that have Direct permissions data on ResourcePaths.
Solution_Comment__c: Slight NEA performance issue due to excessive data and unexpectedly long processing time.
